cs.SI, cs.CY, cs.IR, cs.DB, cs.LG

Reasoning: 
- cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) is the most likely category as the paper deals with using public business data from Facebook to recommend zones for physical businesses. 
- cs.CY (Computers and Society) is also likely as the paper discusses the impact of urban planning on businesses. 
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is relevant as the paper uses machine learning algorithms to recommend zones for businesses based on their metadata. 
- cs.DB (Databases) is relevant as the paper deals with handling and analyzing large amounts of business data. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also relevant as the paper uses machine learning algorithms to make recommendations.
